parameters:
I'm curious about what's happening next door.
There might be someone there, so it's dangerous to
go out now.

Phew... It took quite a while, but it looks like
the preparations are finally coming to an end.

(I'm not sure how much time has passed since then,
but the ritual hasn't been performed yet.)
(I have finally fully recovered my magical power)

(With this, I can finally fight Jackson. It's not
what I wanted, but thanks to the loop, I've been
getting stronger little by little.)

(Amelia and Elena are here too. If we're in
perfect condition, this time I won't lose.)

(The escape from the prison has also been resolved
through prior preparations)

(Because I received a magical tool that can unlock
the door when I met Chloe in this loop)

(It was a miscalculation that I can't use it
without injecting magical power, but this much is
not a problem)

(I knew from the previous loop that Jackson would
put me in prison without laying a hand on me)

(So, I chose a method that can definitely defeat
him)

(Even if I knew Amelia would have a terrible
experience...)

It's okay... Even if Amelia goes through something
terrible, she won't break.
In the end, I will definitely make you happy.

The infusion of magic power is almost ready...
Hm... I hear a sound from next door.
This is Elena's voice... Is she doing something?
Wait, I'm putting on clothes now.

Magic to open locks? You can use something like
that?

No, it's a magical tool. I got it at the club
building.

But I had to infuse it with magic power to use it,
so it took a little time.
Ah... Did you hear what I asked earlier?
Ah... I was next to you.

It's not something that Kohshin needs to apologize
for. But... I wonder if it's still embarrassing.

Even though I was determined to stop Senpai, I
completely turned into a woman.
I think it can't be helped.

I feel bad for asking for help, but I'll wait
here.
I'll just be a burden if I go with you.

Yeah, it's true. The reason I joined the Magic
Research Club was also to have sex.

After all is said and done, that was the most
shocking thing.

When I was accepted into the club, I was happy
because I thought my talent had been recognized.

I can only use healing magic properly, so there's
no way I have any talent.
I should have realized it sooner.

Healing magic is not a magic that anyone can use.
It's impressive just to be able to use it.

Besides, both Amelia and I have been saved by
Elena's healing magic.
I think you should have more confidence.

So, if you're willing, I want you to help me
defeat Jackson.

But... I was happy. It was the first time someone
told me that I was necessary.
If you're telling me to come with you, I'll go.
Because I don't want to just be told.

Ah, I'll teach Jackson about Elena's magical
talent.
First, we need to find Amelia.

(From what I can see, her clothes aren't
disheveled and she doesn't seem to have been
touched...)

The ritual hasn't started yet, let's go stop it
right away.
Yeah, my magical power is at its peak.
Both of you have a strange smell.
Maybe it's the smell of semen...

That is... No, it's not like that. I haven't done
anything.
Of course. I've... been through various things.

I see... I'm sorry. But, since I've also done it
with Masamune-kun...

Why are you doubting it? There's no way Elena and
Kosumi would have sex.

Besides, now is not the time to be saying such
things.

That's right. We need to hurry or the ritual will
begin.

I see... I wanted to feel refreshed before the
battle too.

I'm feeling quite horny too... I want to have sex
too...
I'm saying that I haven't done it.

Amelia, this is not the time to be making strange
jokes.
Ahaha... Sorry, forget what I just said.
Now, let's go stop Jackson and the others.

(I didn't think she had a personality to make such
jokes)
Anyway, let's hurry to the representative room.

There's no time to waste reading help. We'll stop
them ourselves.
